    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-06-21</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-07-19T21:48:50Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a tax credit for the production of biomethane from biomass and make such credit amount equal to the tax credit for producing electricity from biomass; and (2) include biomethane facilities as qualified facilities for purposes of the tax credit for producing electricity from renewable resources.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to provide a credit against income tax for biomethane produced from biomass which is equivalent to the credit allowed for electricity produced from biomass.</title>
